# AI Agent Implementation Prompt
## Reusable Template — Based on "Nila" Workplace Request Management System

Use this file as a blueprint to add AI agents, intelligent chat assistants, and voice interaction to **any web application**.

**Source stack:**
- Backend: FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + LangGraph + LangChain (DeepSeek / OpenAI)
- Frontend: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS + framer-motion

