Build a 4-node LangGraph StateGraph pipeline with the following nodes:

  ┌─ Node 1: parse_intent ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  │  • Call an LLM (DeepSeek or OpenAI) to analyse the user's free-text message.
  │  • Detect intent from this list (replace with your domain intents):
  │      ["create", "track", "approve", "general"]
  │      e.g. for HR: ["apply_leave","check_payslip","raise_grievance","general"]
  │  • Extract domain entities: item name, category, priority, date, etc.
  │  • Detect language: "en" (English) or "ta" (Tamil) or "hi" (Hindi) — add your languages.
  │  • Return ONLY a JSON object. Strip markdown code fences before json.loads().
  │  • Fallback to keyword matching if the LLM call raises any exception.
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  ┌─ Node 2: policy ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  │  • Validate extracted entities against an allowed-values list.
  │  • If invalid → set policy_valid=False and policy_message with reason.
  │  • If valid   → set policy_valid=True.
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  ┌─ Node 3: execution ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  │  • Map intent to a UI navigation action string, e.g.:
  │      "open_form", "open_list", "open_approvals", "general_response"
  │  • Build a `prefill` dict with field values to pre-populate on the target page.
  │  • Do NOT write to the database here — keep API endpoints responsible for writes.
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  ┌─ Node 4: output ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  │  • Generate a short, friendly response string in the user's detected language.
  │  • Support English + at least one additional language (Tamil shown as example).
  │  • If policy_valid=False, reply apologetically with the policy reason.
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

