## ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM

```
User types / speaks
       │
       ▼
React Widget (useVoice hook)
       │  POST /api/agent  { user_input, language }
       ▼
FastAPI endpoint  ← JWT-protected
       │
       ▼
LangGraph agent_graph.invoke(state)
  ├── Node 1: LLM parses intent + extracts entities
  ├── Node 2: Policy validates entities
  ├── Node 3: Execution builds UI action + prefill
  └── Node 4: Output generates natural language response
       │
       │  { intent, action, prefill, response_text, language }
       ▼
React Widget
  ├── Displays response text in chat bubble
  ├── Navigates to correct page with prefill data
  └── speak(response_text, language)  ← Web Speech API TTS
```

