## QUICK-START CHECKLIST

1. Copy `backend/agent/workflow.py` into your project and adapt intents/entities.
2. Add `/api/agent` POST endpoint to your FastAPI `main.py`.
3. Add `AgentRequest` / `AgentResponse` Pydantic models to `schemas.py`.
4. Copy `frontend/src/components/Nila/` to your project and rename the folder.
5. Copy `frontend/src/hooks/useVoice.js` as-is (no changes needed).
6. Set `DEEPSEEK_API_KEY` or `OPENAI_API_KEY` in your `.env`.
7. Run `pip install langgraph langchain langchain-openai openai httpx python-dotenv`.
8. Mount `<YourAssistantWidget />` inside your authenticated layout component.
9. Done — the agent is live!

